            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Hd1e108">Rubrica 27</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De penitentia et congtritione peccatorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>¶ De penitentia et contritio
      <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>ne peccatorum. Rubrica. 27
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/> <ref>PSalmista. 3 psalmus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e125">Be <!-- "bexta" should be "juxta"-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>xta est domi
        <lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>nus his qui tribulato sunt cor
        <lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>de et humiles spiritu saluabit. Mul. <!-- what is the abbreviation for "Mul."?-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>te tribulationes instorum: et de his omnibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>liberabit eos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e139"> /
               <ref>146 pslamus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e141">Qui seminant in la
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>chrymis in exultatione metent. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>
               ¶ <ref>Ezechiel propheta.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e152">Si impius egerit peni
        <lb ed="#V" n="56" break="no"/>tentiam ab omnibus peccatis suis que ope
        <lb ed="#V" n="57" break="no"/>ratus est et custodierit omnia precepta mea
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>et fecerit iudicium et iustitiam: vita viuet et
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>non morietur: omnium iniquitatum eius:
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>quas: operatus est: non recordabor ait do
        <lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>minus. Conuertimini et agite penitentiam
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>ab omnibus iniquitatibus vestris: et non
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>erit vobis in ruinam iniquitas. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e173">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
               ¶ <ref>Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiasti. ca. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e177">Altis
        <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>simus odio habet peccatores: et misertus est
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>penitentibus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e185">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>
               ¶ <ref>Mattheus in euangelio. c. 3. et. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e189">Peni
        <lb ed="#V" n="68" break="no"/>tentiam agite: appropinquabit enim regnum
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>celorum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e197"> /
               <ref>c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e199">Beati qui lugent quoniam
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>ipsi consolabuntur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e205">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
               ¶ <ref>Lucas in euangelio: capitulo tertio.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e209">Fa
        <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>cite dignos fructus penitentie. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e215"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e217"> Idem in
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>actibus apostolorum capitulo tertio. Pe
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>niteamini et conuertimini vt deleantur pec
        <lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>cata vestra. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e228">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e232">¶ Paulus apostolus epistola. 2. ad corin
        <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>thinos capitulo. 7. Que enim secundum deum tristitia
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>est: penitentiam in salutem stabilem ope
        <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>ratur. Seculi autem tristitia mortem ope
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>ratur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e244">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
               ¶ <ref>Seneca tragediarum in agamenone capi
               <lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>tulo. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e248">Quem penitet peccasse pene est in
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>nocens. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e256"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e258"> Idem de naturalibus questio
        <lb ed="#V" n="84" break="no"/>nibus libro secundo: Fidelissimus est qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>ad honesta ex penitentia transit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e266">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
               ¶ <ref>Cecilius firmianus de beata vita libro. 3</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e270">
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>Multo firmior est fides quam reponit pe
        <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>nitentia. <!--47.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="10-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e284">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
               ¶ <ref>Isidorus in sinonima soliloquiorum li. i. ca
               <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e288">Facile penitentibus diuia clementia sub
        <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>uenit. Per penitentiam indulgentia datur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>Per penitentiam delicta omnia absterguntur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e298">
               <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>
               / <ref>16. c. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e302">Inanis est penitentia quam culpa se
        <lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>quens coinquinat </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
